{"tid":1302994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔「連儂牆」繼續張貼可能涉及警員編號及姓名圖片","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:45:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bc61c299b2af0e42c6e4c98764c84dc41349cd6b","tid":1302994,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"根據網上片段，在大埔墟港鐵站附近行人隧道的「連儂牆」，凌晨有多名手持盾牌的警員，到場撕下牆上部分紙張及圖片。本台向警方查詢了解事件，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n記者早上到場所見，「連儂牆」上大部分便條已被膠膜封好，繼續有市民寫上字句。現場可見，可能涉及警員編號及姓名的圖片，被貼在隧道內。<br />\n<br />\n期間一名男子因撕下「連儂牆」上的字條，引來在場市民不滿，雙方一度發生口角。有市民說，支持設立「連儂牆」，可讓大家有渠道發洩怨氣，但不贊成涉及人身攻擊，亦不應將警員個人資料公開。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467602-20190710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467602-20190710.htm&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8034a9c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467602-20190710.htm&h=80b8a395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467602-20190710.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f6ba6c0d78fbe8f74736eec0f9899a06a230d5e9","tid":1302994,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"歡迎入嚟討論<br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299934</a>"},{"pid":"0b3e7798f133d838cb00221576889c914868f567","tid":1302994,"uid":254371,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話撚左會撕一貼萬<br />\n班撕紙狗都冇撚腦</span></span>"},{"pid":"8cc691c5375ae298fea4b67b718e5a345325e943","tid":1302994,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3e7798f133d838cb00221576889c914868f567","tid":1302994,"uid":254371,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-1